-- Atlantia Chief Executive Sees Emerging Markets Opportunities, FT Reports
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-06-21T01:44:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/atlantia-chief-executive-sees-emerging-markets-opportunities-ft-reports.html

          
          
             Atlantia SpA  Chief Executive Officer
 Giovanni Castellucci  said that he expected the toll road company
to make acquisitions of smaller companies in emerging markets,
with India presenting particular opportunities, the Financial
Times reported, citing an interview.  
 Bids may also involve financial institutions, the FT
reported him as saying.  
